                            Anonymous
                            <span class="pull-right">10 days ago</span>
                            <p>GRID is a good arcade-simulation game. No worries on car-settings, just sit behind the wheel, push the gas and race. You will smell petrol and smoke, you will see tyre-particles on windshield while pushing it to the limits. Not recommended for those who like to setup the car under the hood, but ideal if you just want a good ride. 4 star is I'm also missing the possibility to fine-tuning and upgrading the car.</p>
